Morning all.

Anyone loves this kueh shop at Wisma Atria?

I still remember like when I was a kid, my parents will always bring us to this shop to takeaway tapioca kuehs and onde onde.

This was when Wisma used to be old school back then.

This stall still looks so traditional. And most times if you are hurrying to Taka, you may miss this hole in the wall gem.
